{"id":145076,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/要搞紅色頻道-重慶衛視被迫裁員/","date":"2011-04-17T05:30:14Z","modified":"2011-04-17T05:30:14Z","title":"要搞紅色頻道 重慶衛視被迫裁員","content":"<p>今年1月和3月，重慶衛視大改版，一切遵照市委書記薄熙來的「唱紅」主旋律。結果不到1個半月，重慶衛視收視大跌，廣告紛紛棄重慶衛視而去，搞得重慶衛視的廣告中心現在被迫減員20%，採編人員也將減薪。</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=752465\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Subscribe me!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[9587]}